### Upload Single Media File (Raw Body)
# Uploads a single image to the media store as raw request body.
# Supported Content-Types: image/jpeg, image/jpg, image/png, application/octet-stream
# @name uploadSingleMedia
POST {{host}}/api/media/upload/single
Content-Type: image/jpeg
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

< /path/to/your/image.jpg

### Expected Response (Success - 200 OK):
# Content-Type: application/json
#
# {
#   "id": "697d1a636b00a21a27f1b1b4",
#   "filename": "uuid",
#   "extension": "jpg",
#   "dateTime": "2026-01-30T20:53:55Z",
#   "path": "/uuid.jpg",
#   "xsThumbPath": "/thumbs-xs/uuid.jpg",
#   "smThumbPath": "/thumbs-sm/uuid.jpg",
