### Get Media File
# Retrieves a media file (original or thumbnail) from the store.
# @name getMedia
GET {{host}}/api/media?p=/path/to/image.jpg

### Expected Response (Success - 200 OK):
# Content-Type: image/jpeg (or appropriate mimetype)
# (Binary image data)

### Expected Response (Error - 404 Not Found):
# If the file does not exist.
# HTTP/1.1 404 Not Found